ZAPHOD DAEMON PROTOCOL
2002 July 20

Vino Crescini
jvcrescini@yahoo.com

- Protocol

  Message               Reply
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  count                 n (where n is the number of messages)
  get(n)                message (nth message)
  del(n)                m (where m is the number of messages after message
                           n is deleted)
  put(message)          n (where n is the number of messages after message
                           is added)

- Messages

  The message text itself must have certain characters escaped.

  - Backslash (\) must be escaped to double backslash (\\)
  - Open Parenthesis ( must be escaped to \(
  - Close Parenthesis ) must be escaped to \)
